snippet.title: 東方店舗録 ～ Combinations with you by 魯鈍ジョン
snippet.description:
𝘙𝘦𝘤𝘰𝘮𝘮𝘦𝘯𝘥𝘦𝘥 𝘣𝘺 𝘓𝘦 𝘈𝘨𝘨𝘳𝘦𝘴𝘴𝘰𝘳

The fight against FamilyMart Murasa here is a bit of a tough one at first, but gets easier as you continue to do better against her. Ultimately when fighting her the most important thing is to watch out for and prepare for three particularly difficult spell cards she pulls off. You may start with very few resources, but this game’s quite generous with them as you play through the game so it’s not terribly difficult to stockpile for the more difficult attacks.

Character: Suwako Moriya
Boss: Manager Murasa

Music

♪ Dawn Moon And Double Cherry Blossoms by 桐生
http://www.nicovideo.jp/watch/sm8840567

♪ FamilyMart Clerk Developed Intense Danmaku by 桐生
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wUgHIBmukMM

♪ Song of the Blue Wind 〜 Twinkle Dream by 桐生
http://www.nicovideo.jp/watch/sm10592339

Spell Cards

2:14 - Non-spell
2:26 - Store Sign "Franchise Scarlet"
2:40 - Non-spell
2:52 - Entrance Sign “Automatic Door”
3:17 - Non-spell
3:27 - Sale “Store That Boils for You”
3:41 - Non-spell
3:52 - Reading “Exteeeending Aaaaarm"
4:46 - Non-spell
4:55 - Midnight “Open All Night All Week”
5:21 - Non-spell
5:31 - "Boundary of Manager and Part Timer"
6:07 - Non-spell
6:29 - Bag Bringing “Super Economical”
6:42 - "CHEEEEEEEN Store"
7:42 - “Fragrance of Famous Chicken”

You can download the script here
http://www.mediafire.com/file/zlazymm5dox/famima.zip
